### Create payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Mensalidade Janeiro",
  "value": 99.90,
  "paymentMethod": "Pix",
  "dueDate": "2025-01-10",
  "issueDate": null,
  "status": "A receber",
  "subscriptionId": 1
}

###

### List all payments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by subscription
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments?subscriptionId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by student name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments?studentName=João
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get payment by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update payment
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Mensalidade Janeiro - Pago",
  "value": 99.90,
  "paymentMethod": "Pix",
  "dueDate": "2025-01-10",
  "issueDate": "2025-01-08",
  "status": "Pago",
  "subscriptionId": 1
}

###

### Delete payment
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
